        {
          "block_id": "p10_b1",
          "block_type": "paragraph",
          "text": "I Computing VIF for FAM, PEER, and SCHOOL",
          "bbox": [
            0.101867,
            0.118664,
            0.577565,
            0.053671
          ],
          "reading_order": 1
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p10_b2",
          "block_type": "paragraph",
          "text": "I R2",
          "bbox": [
            0.101867,
            0.181161,
            0.068387,
            0.053671
          ],
          "reading_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p10_b3",
          "block_type": "paragraph",
          "text": "F AM is the multiple R2 obtained from the model :\nFAM = β0 + β1PEER + β2SCHOOL.",
          "bbox": [
            0.138258,
            0.181384,
            0.604379,
            0.100017
          ],
          "reading_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p10_b4",
          "block_type": "paragraph",
          "text": "> fit_F=lm(FAM~PEER+SCHOOL,edu)\n> summary(fit_F)",
          "bbox": [
            0.181226,
            0.305617,
            0.402189,
            0.074972
          ],
          "reading_order": 4
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p10_b5",
          "block_type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Estimate Std. Error t value Pr(>|t|)\n(Intercept)\n0.02088\n0.02156\n0.969\n0.336\nPEER\n-0.26559\n0.12412\n-2.140\n0.036 *\nSCHOOL\n1.27878\n0.11215\n11.402\n<2e-16 ***",
          "bbox": [
            0.181226,
            0.394212,
            0.67464,
            0.163574
          ],
          "reading_order": 5
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p10_b6",
          "block_type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Residual standard error: 0.1793 on 67 degrees of freedom\nMultiple R-squared: 0.9734,\nAdjusted R-squared: 0.9726\nF-statistic:\n1225 on 2 and 67 DF,\np-value: < 2.2e-16",
          "bbox": [
            0.181226,
            0.615709,
            0.726535,
            0.119271
          ],
          "reading_order": 6
        },
        {
